---
// Hero section for the landing page.  Contains the name, title, a short
// introduction, CTA buttons and social links.  The content here can be
// customised to update the value proposition.  All external links open in
// new tabs with appropriate security attributes.
---
<section id="hero" class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-gray-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:via-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
